Editor's note: Livestream courtesy DStv 403, you can also watch it on DStv Now. JOHANNESBURG - Former South African Airways treasurer, Cynthia Stimpel, will take the stand at the State Capture inquiry today. This as the commission turns its attention to the aviation sector. On Wednesday, former NPA head Mxolisi Nxasana's testimony was halted, for now, until implicated parties are given sufficient time to respond to allegations. Nxasana named his then deputy Nomgcobo Jiba in the campaign to remove him from the NPA. READ: Nxasana: There has been political interference at NPA He slammed the conduct of his Jiba in the case involving former KZN Hawks Head Johan Booysen.